nt property, all ministries are informed to enter the details of their own vehicles and the vehicles and other properties under their line offices and agencies in the Public Assets Management System(PAMS) format at the Office of Auditor General within December 30,\u201d the notice issued by the Ministry of Industry Commerce and Supplies reads.\n\nThe Ministry has formed a nine member Auction Management Committee under the coordination of the Auditor General.","title":"Government to auction unnecessary vehicles - Khabarhub","url":"http://english.khabarhub.com/2020/13/148597/","video":[]}
